set_teaching_person
Discworld guild help
set_teaching_person

Name
.SI 5
set_teaching_person - Sets the person who does the teaching.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_teaching_person(string str);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Sets trhe person who does the teaching.  If this is not non zero then
no spells or commands will be taught to the prospective player.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
add_command, add_spell, query_teaching_person
.EP
